e if people do not know ignorance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Taymiyyah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, the bonds of Islam will undone, one by one, only if there arise people in Islam who never knew the time of ignorance.\u201d Source: Majmu\u0304' al-Fata\u0304wa\u0301 15\/54 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062a\u064a\u0645\u064a\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6555,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/umar-converts-to-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":17721,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Umar: The Prophet prays for Umar&#8217;s conversion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, strengthen Islam with one of two men whom you love more: Abu Jahl or Umar ibn al-Khattab.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cThe most beloved of the two was Umar.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3681 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17587,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/